text: It doesn’t mean too much, so probably shouldn’t be a warning. I have noticed those in the tests, but if you are working with a larger network with a lot of messages there would be more. We are making large changes to Gossip, so I would expect these log messages to change in master.
<@U26PBUZRT> Also, I fixed the mktclient exchange command so —type is required by the cli.
